  <section>
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>The <em>Status</em> library provides <em>status codes</em> denoting reasons for the failures of operations.</p>

    <p>The <em>Status</em> library fulfils the <a href="@(baseurl)api/ring1-library/introduction.html">module concept</a>
    but does not require initialization.</p>

    <p>The include file of the <em>Status</em> library is <code class="inline">Ring1/Status.h</code>,
    its library file is <code class="inline">Ring1.lib</code>.</p>
  </section>

